<Base title="Simmer — Support" doc>
  <nav><a href="/simmer/">← Simmer</a></nav>
  <h1>Support</h1>

  <h2>Get in touch</h2>
  <p>Email us at <a href="mailto:support@sunpebblelabs.com">support@sunpebblelabs.com</a> —
     we usually reply within two days.</p>

  <h2>Restore your purchase</h2>
  <p>Reinstalled or got a new phone? Open Simmer → Settings → <em>Restore Purchase</em>.
     The unlock is tied to your Apple ID, so you'll never pay twice.</p>

  <h2>Timers not showing in the Dynamic Island?</h2>
  <p>Make sure Live Activities are enabled in Settings → Simmer → <em>Live Activities</em>.</p>
</Base>
